* GCC target version *

  The omp task patch currently applies against gcc 4.2.2.


* Install steps *

- download and untar gcc-core-4.2.2.tar.bz2

- apply patch:
$ (cd gcc-4.2.2 && patch -p1 < ../tasks.patch)

- make build and install directories:
$ ./make_dirs

- autoreconf libgomp and configure gcc:
$ cd build
$ ../configure

- build and install gcc:
$ make && make install

- build examples:
$ cd ../examples
$ make && make vars

- source vars to get the right LD_LIBRARY_PATH
$ . vars

- run examples:
$ ./task
$ ./taskwait

